		     <div class="instruction instruction1">
		       <ul>
		         <li>
		           <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		             <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>	<!-- added 28/03/18 -->
		             </div>
		             <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              Please understand the child's interests and hobbies in detail and write it down. Look for evidences of activities over a long period of time concerned with that activity.
		             </div>
		           </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		          <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		           <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		           </div>
		           <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              <span>
                       Please check how his/her academic performance- most recent marks, consistency or trends in key subjects like math and science.
		           </span>
		           </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		          <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		             <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"  style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		               <span>
		               Try to get a basic understanding of the nature of the student, from your limited interaction with her / him.- extrovert, introvert, soft spoken, confident, inquisitive, etc.
		               </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		         <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		               <span>
		                 Please discuss the interest and abilities test results with parents and child in S1.
 
		               </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		         <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              <span>
		             Please record / collect from the parents / student their experience with the assessment- simple/ tough/easy to understand instructions etc.
		             </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		         <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              <span>
                          Please try to arrive at a theme for the child.		           
                       </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		         <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              <span>
                           Please set the expectations with the student and the parent about what the Lodestar program offers, what will be covered / done in the 3 sessions and what the parents can expect at the end of the program.		           
                      </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		         <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              <span>
                           Give a brief about the IRs and ORs- what do they contain, key areas covered etc.		           
                       </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		         <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              <span>
                        Please try to create the occupation wish list for the child - occupations basis the color code / fitment; occupations basis the interest the child has shown towards an industry or job while exploring world of jobs; occupations basis the subject of interest and the theme of the child you have understood through your interactions with the child, in addition to what the child chosen. This can be done when there aren't enough occupations chosen by the child.		           
                             </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		         <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              <span>
                           Please gather the response / comment the parent / student made on the WOJs.		           
                             </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         <li>
		         <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              <span>
                      Please observe, gather the list of industries that the student / parent showed interest in.		           
                             </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         
		          <li>
		         <div class="instruction_txt_div">
		            <div class="icon_left_div">
		              <i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" style="margin-left: -12px;"></i>
		            </div>
		            <div class="instruction_right_div">
		              <span>
                      Talk about manual search with the child that the child can search manually and add occupations in the wish list by themselves.		           
                     </span>
		            </div>
		          </div>
		         </li>
		         
		         
		         
		       </ul>
		       
